items.description: Machine Learning framework for Sofa

items.name: -Wine-Quality-Prediction
items.description: This project provides a comprehensive framework for predicting wine quality using machine learning, offering insights and tools that can be valuable for wine producers and enthusiasts alike.

items.name: medAI-ML-practice
items.description: A practical framework applying machine learning techniques to a medical dataset (mammographic mass data), showcasing the potential of ML in healthcare.

items.name: Hypernets
items.description: A General Automated Machine Learning framework to simplify the development of End-to-end AutoML toolkits in specific domains.

items.name: Movie-Recommendation-System-Django-and-ML
items.description: Movie Recommendation System using Django Framework & Machine Learning

items.name: MOFs2Enzyme
items.description: Exploring Enzyme-Mimicking Metal-Organic Frameworks for CO2 Conversion through Vibrational Spectra-based Machine Learning

items.name: LWKNN
items.description: A fingerprint location framework for uneven WiFi signals based on machine learning

items.name: pacmof
items.description: PACMOF is a small and easy to use python library that uses machine Learning to quickly estimate partial atomic charges in  metal-organic frameworks.

items.name: eduApp
items.description: Our EduApp is specifically designed to address the educational challenges faced by rural students. It uses an Angular frontend with robust Express engine facilitating the Node.js framework and uses MongoDB for scalable data handling. To enhance the user experience, we've implemented machine learning techniques with the help of the Gemini Pro model

items.name: JMLR2024
items.description: A code repository for the article "A multilabel classification framework for approximate nearest neighbor search" published in Journal of Machine Learning Research (JMLR) in 02/2024.

items.name: Minor_Project_mca_jims
items.description: Developing a Music Recommendation system based on Machine Learning and Python Django Framework

items.name: AgML
items.description: AgML is a centralized framework for agricultural machine learning. AgML provides access to public agricultural datasets for common agricultural deep learning tasks, with standard benchmarks and pretrained models, as well the ability to generate synthetic data and annotations.

items.name: causal-npi-effects
items.description: A causal machine learning framework to assess effects of non-pharmaceutical interventions on pandemic disease spread.

items.name: AIfES_for_Arduino
items.description: This is the Arduino compatible port of the AIfES machine learning framework, developed and maintained by Fraunhofer Institute for Microelectronic Circuits and Systems.

license.name: GNU Affero General Public License v3.0

items.name: algorithm-serving-framework
items.description: This project's goal is to offer a reusable framework for deploying machine learning algorithms. The finished project should allow a user to upload, manage, deploy, and monitor a machine learning algorithm. The chosen model format is ONNX, other compatibilities are welcome.

items.name: educational_projects
items.description: This repository contains projects carried out within the framework of the master's program Big Data and Machine Learning

items.name: Healthify
items.description: Prediction of 5 Various Diseases using different Machine Learning Models implemented using a Django Framework which is a popular Web Development Framework in Python

items.name: coracle
items.description: Machine Learning Framework to Identify Coral Bacteria Associated with Thermal Resilience

items.name: Conversational-AutoML
items.description: A Framework for Generating an Efficient Machine Learning Model with a Few Sentences

items.name: kotlin_machine_learning_lifecycle_framework
items.description: Kotlin-based machine learning lifecycle framework

items.name: orchid
items.description: A novel management, annotation, and machine learning framework for analyzing cancer mutations

items.name: CNN_Skin_Lesion_Detector_Project
items.description: Skin Lesion Detection App made with Flutter Framework and Dart Language, as a project for my CS334 - Algorithms of Machine Learning Class.

items.name: TrialTranslator
items.description: Framework for in-silico reproduction of landmark oncology randomized controlled trials using machine learning survival models.

items.name: predicting-fraud-with-tensorflow
items.description: Predicting Fraud with TensorFlow" is a machine learning project aimed at developing and implementing fraud detection models using TensorFlow, a popular deep learning framework.

items.name: Agile-Development-with-Azure
items.description: A project to demonstrate and perform continuous delivery for a Python-based machine learning application using the Flask web framework.

items.name: QML-frameworks
items.description: Reviews of quantum machine learning frameworks pennylane and TensorFlow Quantum

items.name: Stroke-Prediction
items.description: This project involves the development of a Dockerized RESTful API for predicting stroke occurrence based on a dataset using a Random Forest machine learning model. The project utilizes the Flask framework in Python to create the API endpoints, allowing seamless interaction with the model.

items.name: Automated-Fall-Detection-Using-Smartphone-Sensors
items.description: The development of a system, utilizing smartphone and smartwatch inertial sensors, and introduces a machine learning framework for identifying and classifying elderly activities, with a specific focus on fall detection.

items.name: Counterfactual-Generation-with-Answer-Set-Programming
items.description: Contains the code where we use our CFGS Framework to generate counterfactuals from rRule-based-machine-learning algorithms
